<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 06:10:50 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>如果耶路撒冷日是以色列社会的精确温度计，那么今年的诊断已经结束</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/if-jerusalem-day-is-an-accurate-thermometer-of-israeli-society-the-diagnosis-is-terminal/0000018f-eab4-d463-a19f-ffbd44ad0000</link><description>前几年，官员们做出了一些努力来平息事态。今年，年轻人似乎可以随意呼喊种族主义口号、骚乱以及攻击他们遇到的任何人。耶路撒冷统一五十七年后，经过八个月的战争，以色列领导层希望我们能通过复仇而不是希望来凑合</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 03:09:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/if-jerusalem-day-is-an-accurate-thermometer-of-israeli-society-the-diagnosis-is-terminal/0000018f-eab4-d463-a19f-ffbd44ad0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和真主党之间的边缘政策可能将双方推向边缘</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/brinkmanship-between-israel-and-hezbollah-could-push-both-sides-over-the-edge/0000018f-e9f1-dc46-a5bf-f9f58e310000</link><description>以色列总参谋部努力向真主党展示全面战争将带来的代价。对黎巴嫩的破坏将是巨大的，但对以色列北部和中部城市可能造成的破坏与哈马斯所经历的任何破坏都不一样</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 03:00:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/brinkmanship-between-israel-and-hezbollah-could-push-both-sides-over-the-edge/0000018f-e9f1-dc46-a5bf-f9f58e310000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在周三黎巴嫩边境附近的无人机袭击中受伤身亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article-live/israel-terrorists-who-took-part-in-october-7-massacre-killed-in-strike-on-hamas-compound/0000018f-eb4c-d4cf-abcf-ef4d922b0000</link><description>在以色列北部的无人机袭击中，11 人受伤，其中一人伤势严重；真主党声称对此事负责 ■ 哈马斯领导人称将“严肃而积极”地处理任何基于全面停战的协议 ■ 以色列秘密针对美国立法者开展加沙战争影响力活动 ■ 黎巴嫩报道：袭击者向美国大使馆开枪，被逮捕黎巴嫩军队士兵 ■ 以色列内阁授权以色列国防军在8月底前将预备役人员人数增加到35万人</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 02:18:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article-live/israel-terrorists-who-took-part-in-october-7-massacre-killed-in-strike-on-hamas-compound/0000018f-eb4c-d4cf-abcf-ef4d922b0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡像夜里的小偷一样潜入什莫纳城。但他害怕的是市长，而不是真主党</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-snuck-into-kiryat-shmona-but-its-the-mayor-he-fears-not-hezbollah/0000018f-ea61-d4cf-abcf-ee61348b0000</link><description>一位小政客，令我们感到羞耻的是，他被称为“总理”，他拒绝会见这座陷入困境的北方城市的市长。内塔尼亚胡的战争时间表是为了满足他的政治需要而量身定制的，他的政府从未显得如此脱节和迟钝</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 22:13:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-snuck-into-kiryat-shmona-but-its-the-mayor-he-fears-not-hezbollah/0000018f-ea61-d4cf-abcf-ee61348b0000</guid></item><item><title>真主党无人机袭击以色列北部，造成十二人受伤，其中一人伤势严重</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/twelve-wounded-one-critically-by-hezbollah-drone-strike-in-northern-israel/0000018f-e9d8-da58-a1ef-f9dacca50000</link><description>以色列国防军正在调查为什么袭击前没有响起警报。真主党声称对此负责，称这是对以色列前一天在黎巴嫩南部发动袭击的回应</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 19:47:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/twelve-wounded-one-critically-by-hezbollah-drone-strike-in-northern-israel/0000018f-e9d8-da58-a1ef-f9dacca50000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔呼吁允许犹太人在圣殿山祈祷；内塔尼亚胡：现状“不会改变”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-calls-for-jews-to-pray-on-temple-mount-netanyahu-status-quo-will-not-change/0000018f-e9af-d463-a19f-fdbffea90000</link><description>这是以色列负责圣殿山/阿克萨清真寺安全的部长第一次公开背离该地点禁止犹太人在那里祈祷的现行现状。内塔尼亚胡总理很快反驳了极右翼部长的言论</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 19:45:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-calls-for-jews-to-pray-on-temple-mount-netanyahu-status-quo-will-not-change/0000018f-e9af-d463-a19f-fdbffea90000</guid></item><item><title>他们生活在一个遥远的星球上。但不幸的是，对于以色列来说，他们负责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-05/ty-article/.highlight/they-live-on-a-far-off-planet-but-unfortunately-for-israel-theyre-in-charge/0000018f-e971-da58-a1ef-f9f3967a0000</link><description>越来越多的情况是，总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的联盟成员似乎生活在某个遥远的星球上：在这个星球上，没有任何一个负责的成年人是错的，所说的事情使它们成为事实，而忽视问题则使问题消失</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 19:02:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-05/ty-article/.highlight/they-live-on-a-far-off-planet-but-unfortunately-for-israel-theyre-in-charge/0000018f-e971-da58-a1ef-f9f3967a0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡和以色列将军秘密希望结束加沙战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-and-israels-generals-secretly-want-to-end-the-gaza-war/0000018f-e90c-d4cf-abcf-ef4d8e330000</link><description>首相总是希望有尽可能多的选择，他得出的结论是，他需要一个结束战争的选择。但他停止战斗的动机与他的将军们不同</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 17:34:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-and-israels-generals-secretly-want-to-end-the-gaza-war/0000018f-e90c-d4cf-abcf-ef4d8e330000</guid></item><item><title>在以色列校园里，犹太和巴勒斯坦学生创造了理智和希望的时刻</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/on-an-israeli-campus-jewish-and-palestinian-students-carve-out-moments-of-sanity-and-hope/0000018f-e805-d0ea-a1bf-fb45d2c60000</link><description>在特拉维夫大学的 MiddleMeets 倡议中，阿拉伯和犹太学生互相谈论大屠杀、10 月 7 日大浩劫和加沙轰炸。目标：不放弃。它也能在美国校园的战场上发挥作用吗？</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 17:08:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/on-an-israeli-campus-jewish-and-palestinian-students-carve-out-moments-of-sanity-and-hope/0000018f-e805-d0ea-a1bf-fb45d2c60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 243 天：哈马斯与法塔赫之间的和解谈判定于 6 月中旬进行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-243-reconciliation-talks-between-hamas-fatah-set-for-june/0000018f-e957-dda1-a99f-ebd7182d0001</link><description>内塔尼亚胡表示，以色列“准备对真主党采取非常有力的行动” ■ 政府将投票授权以色列国防军在 8 月底前将现役预备役军人人数增加到 35 万人 ■ 武装人员向贝鲁特附近的美国大使馆开枪 ■ 哈马斯与以色列之间的和解谈判巴勒斯坦总统阿巴斯的法塔赫晚会将于 6 月中旬在中国举行 ■ 战争进入 243 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 17:05:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-243-reconciliation-talks-between-hamas-fatah-set-for-june/0000018f-e957-dda1-a99f-ebd7182d0001</guid></item><item><title>2006年黎巴嫩战争中被烧毁的以色列北部大片森林再次燃烧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/vast-areas-of-northern-israels-forests-burned-in-the-2006-lebanon-war-burn-again/0000018f-e92f-dc46-a5bf-f9efcea40000</link><description>JNF 上加利利地区主管表示，现在正值夏季，落在森林中的每一片弹片都会引发火灾。根据JNF的数据，过去几天北部地区的烧毁面积至少是整个第二次黎巴嫩战争期间的两倍</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 17:04:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/vast-areas-of-northern-israels-forests-burned-in-the-2006-lebanon-war-burn-again/0000018f-e92f-dc46-a5bf-f9efcea40000</guid></item><item><title>针对 Radiohead：为什么妖魔化以色列人和犹太人的抵制者不能让我闭嘴</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-05/ty-article-opinion/targeting-radiohead-why-the-boycotters-demonizing-israelis-and-jews-wont-silence-me/0000018f-e887-dfee-ad8f-ef8fc8de0000</link><description>一场亲巴勒斯坦运动的目标是我的丈夫、Radiohead 吉他手乔尼·格林伍德 (Jonny Greenwood)，取消他与以色列音乐家杜杜·塔萨 (Dudu Tassa) 的音乐会。这是一场简单化宣传战的一部分，试图将以色列人从公共广场上抹去</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 15:43:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-05/ty-article-opinion/targeting-radiohead-why-the-boycotters-demonizing-israelis-and-jews-wont-silence-me/0000018f-e887-dfee-ad8f-ef8fc8de0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么加沙战争后以色列北部将不再一样</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/why-israels-north-wont-be-the-same-after-the-gaza-war/0000018f-e8dc-dba5-afdf-fade69e80000</link><description>本周的森林火灾是对以色列北部地区的最新经济打击，在持续的导弹和火箭弹袭击下，该地区正在失去人员、就业机会和企业。而且，看不到尽头</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 15:01:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/why-israels-north-wont-be-the-same-after-the-gaza-war/0000018f-e8dc-dba5-afdf-fade69e80000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗威胁以色列“将为以色列所谓的导致叙利亚顾问死亡的袭击付出代价”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/iran-threatens-israel-will-pay-for-alleged-israeli-strike-that-killed-adviser-in-syria/0000018f-e861-dc46-a5bf-f8e53fc70000</link><description>伊朗革命卫队将军侯赛因·萨拉米誓言，以色列将为这场流血事件付出代价。四月在大马士革</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 13:50:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/iran-threatens-israel-will-pay-for-alleged-israeli-strike-that-killed-adviser-in-syria/0000018f-e861-dc46-a5bf-f8e53fc70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列法院缩短政府下令关闭以色列半岛电视台的期限</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-court-shortens-length-of-govt-ordered-shutdown-of-al-jazeera-in-israel/0000018f-e839-dfee-ad8f-efbdf2a10000</link><description>特拉维夫地区法院下令将半岛电视台关闭的期限从 45 天缩短至 35 天，并于周日到期。该裁决使半岛电视台能够恢复在以色列的正常活动</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 13:40:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-court-shortens-length-of-govt-ordered-shutdown-of-al-jazeera-in-israel/0000018f-e839-dfee-ad8f-efbdf2a10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列“可能拥有世界上最有道德的军队，但不是最有道德的领导力”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-may-have-the-worlds-most-moral-army-but-not-the-most-moral-leadership/0000018f-e3f2-d6db-a7bf-efff60d10000</link><description>研究民主如何消亡的专家金·莱恩·谢佩勒教授对国际刑事法院要求对内塔尼亚胡及其国防部长发出逮捕令并不感到惊讶。她解释了为什么削弱以色列的司法机构只会加强国际刑事法院的案件</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 12:39:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-may-have-the-worlds-most-moral-army-but-not-the-most-moral-leadership/0000018f-e3f2-d6db-a7bf-efff60d10000</guid></item><item><title>Radiohead 吉他手顶住了 BDS 与以色列艺术家合作的压力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/radiohead-guitarist-pushes-back-against-bds-pressure-for-collaboration-with-israeli-artist/0000018f-e81b-d6de-a7df-fe3b70a60000</link><description>英国吉他手兼摇滚乐队 Radiohead 成员乔尼·格林伍德 (Jonny Greenwood) 正在与老朋友兼合作者、以色列著名音乐家杜杜·塔萨 (Dudu Tassa) 一起在欧洲巡演。面对 BDS 取消巡演的压力，格林伍德称批评者“不进步”</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 12:17:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/radiohead-guitarist-pushes-back-against-bds-pressure-for-collaboration-with-israeli-artist/0000018f-e81b-d6de-a7df-fe3b70a60000</guid></item><item><title>女人质？加沙战争？这位以色列极右翼议员担心的是其他事情：未婚女性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/hostages-gaza-war-this-israeli-mk-is-worried-about-something-else-unmarried-women/0000018f-e81c-d1da-adaf-fd9fd3f40000</link><description>奥兹玛·耶胡迪特议员利莫尔·桑·哈尔·梅莱赫在以色列议会核心小组会议上哀叹的不是被关押在加沙的以色列人质的命运，而是极端正统派妇女面临的最严重问题：找不到丈夫</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 12:06:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/hostages-gaza-war-this-israeli-mk-is-worried-about-something-else-unmarried-women/0000018f-e81c-d1da-adaf-fd9fd3f40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列称将把斯德泰曼拘留中心改造成短期拘留设施，减少巴勒斯坦囚犯数量</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-turns-sde-teiman-into-short-term-holding-facility-with-fewer-palestinian-prisoners/0000018f-e7f4-d11f-a5cf-e7ff66cc0000</link><description>在向以色列最高法院提交有关斯德泰曼设施拘留条件的请愿书后，法官要求该州提供有关囚犯条件的答案。该州告知法院，他们正在转移囚犯并改善条件</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 11:30:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-turns-sde-teiman-into-short-term-holding-facility-with-fewer-palestinian-prisoners/0000018f-e7f4-d11f-a5cf-e7ff66cc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列秘密针对美国立法者发起加沙战争影响力活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-06-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-secretly-targeted-american-lawmakers-with-gaza-war-influence-campaign/0000018f-e7c8-d11f-a5cf-e7cb62af0000</link><description>为了影响全球公众对加沙战争的看法，虚假账户和网站传播亲以色列和仇视伊斯兰教的内容。该行动由以色列侨民事务部精心策划，并由一家政治竞选公司运营</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 10:08:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-06-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-secretly-targeted-american-lawmakers-with-gaza-war-influence-campaign/0000018f-e7c8-d11f-a5cf-e7cb62af0000</guid></item></channel></rss>